      <h1 class="text-[2.5rem] md:text-[3.25rem] font-bold mb-6 leading-[1.12]">What Is a Postpartum Doula and Do You Need One?</h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-tjb-gray leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
        A <strong>postpartum doula</strong> is a trained professional who comes to your home after your baby arrives and helps you through the hardest, most beautiful weeks of your life. Not to deliver your baby. Not to replace your partner. To make sure you recover, adjust, and actually get to enjoy your newborn instead of just surviving them.
